// Loot tables keyed by MonsterId. Each entry maps an ItemId to its
// independent drop chance in percent (0–100). On kill the engine
// rolls every line of the matching table separately, so the values
// are *not* weights — a 10/1 row gives a 10% chance for the first
// item AND a 1% chance for the second, both rollable in the same
// kill.
{
  "MONSTER000001": {
    "ITEM000001": 10,
    "ITEM000002": 1
  },
  "MONSTER000002": {
    "ITEM000001": 50,
    "ITEM000002": 20
  }
}
